// METARз‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪйҸҲе¶…е§ҹ - ж·ҮоҶјоҳІINHGз’ҮиҜІеҪҮйҚңеұҪгҒүе§ҳж–ҫе”¬йҗ®дҪҪР’йҸӢ?class METARParser {
  static parse(metarString: string): ParsedMETAR {
    const parsed: ParsedMETAR = {
      station: '',
      time: '',
      windDirection: '',
      windSpeed: '',
      windGust: '',
      windUnit: '',
      visibility: '',
      weather: [],
      temperature: '',
      dewpoint: '',
      pressure: '',
      pressureUnit: 'hPa',
      clouds: [],
      raw: metarString
    };

    if (!metarString) return parsed;

    try {
      // йҚ©зғҳж№°METARз‘ҷпҪҶзҖ„1Ө7
      const parts = metarString.split(' ');
      parsed.station = parts[0];
      
      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪйҸғе •жЈҝ (DDHHMMZ)
      const timeMatch = metarString.match(/(\d{6})Z/);
      if (timeMatch) {
        parsed.time = timeMatch[1];
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪжӨӢ?      const windMatch = metarString.match(/(\d{3}|VRB)(\d{2,3})(G(\d{2,3}))?(KT|MPS)/);
      if (windMatch) {
        parsed.windDirection = windMatch[1];
        parsed.windSpeed = windMatch[2];
        parsed.windGust = windMatch[4] || '';
        parsed.windUnit = windMatch[5];
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪй‘іеҖҹоқҶжҗ„1Ө7?      const visMatch = metarString.match(/(\d{4})(?=\s)/);
      if (visMatch) {
        parsed.visibility = visMatch[1];
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪжҫ¶в•ӮзҡөйҗңжӢҢи–„1Ө7 - йҸўгзЎ…з№ҳжҫ¶в•Ӯзҡөжө пҪҮзҲңз‘ҷпҪҶзҖ„1Ө7
      const weatherCodes = ['BR', 'FG', 'HZ', 'FU', 'VA', 'DU', 'SA', 'SS', 'DS', 'SG', 'IC', 'PL', 'GR', 'GS', 'UP', 'RA', 'DZ', 'SN', 'SQ', 'FC', 'TS', 'MI', 'PR', 'BC', 'DR', 'BL', 'SH', 'VCTS', 'VCSH', 'VCFG', '\\+', '\\-'];
      const weatherRegex = new RegExp(`\\b(${weatherCodes.join('|')})+\\b`, 'g');
      const weatherMatches = metarString.match(weatherRegex);
      if (weatherMatches) {
        parsed.weather = weatherMatches;
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪеЁ“в•Ғе®і/й—ҮиҢ¬еҒ„1Ө7
      const tempMatch = metarString.match(/(M?\d{2})\/(M?\d{2})/);
      if (tempMatch) {
        parsed.temperature = tempMatch[1].replace('M', '-');
        parsed.dewpoint = tempMatch[2].replace('M', '-');
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪе§ҳж–ҝеёҮ - ж·ҮоҶјоҳІINHGз’ҮиҜІеҪҮй—ӮоҮўго•„1Ө7
      const pressureMatchQNH = metarString.match(/Q(\d{4})/);
      const pressureMatchINHG = metarString.match(/A(\d{4})/);
      
      if (pressureMatchQNH) {
        parsed.pressure = pressureMatchQNH[1];
        parsed.pressureUnit = 'hPa';
      } else if (pressureMatchINHG) {
        // зҒҸе—ҡе«ізўгөе‘ҠзқҳйҸҢиҫ«жөҶйҺ№оқӯиҙҹйҗ§жғ§з¬—йҸ„еү§гҒҡй”ӣеұҪжӮ“йҸғжңөз№ҡйҗЈж¬Ҹеё«жҝ®е¬ӘвӮ„1Ө7?        const inhgValue = parseInt(pressureMatchINHG[1]) / 100;
        const hPaValue = Math.round(inhgValue * 33.8639);
        parsed.pressure = `${hPaValue} (${inhgValue.toFixed(2)} INHG)`;
        parsed.pressureUnit = 'INHG';
      }

      // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪжөңжҲҰеҷә - йҸўгзЎ…з№ҳжөңжҲқзң°жө пҪҮзҲңз‘ҷпҪҶзҖ„1Ө7
      const cloudRegex = /(FEW|SCT|BKN|OVC|NSC|SKC|CLR|VV)(\d{3})?/g;
      let cloudMatch;
      while ((cloudMatch = cloudRegex.exec(metarString)) !== null) {
        if (cloudMatch[1] === 'NSC' || cloudMatch[1] === 'SKC' || cloudMatch[1] === 'CLR') {
          // йҸғзҠұз°ҜйҺҜе‘ӯе–Ң
          parsed.clouds.push({
            type: cloudMatch[1],
            height: '0'
          });
        } else {
          parsed.clouds.push({
            type: cloudMatch[1],
            height: cloudMatch[2] ? (parseInt(cloudMatch[2]) * 100).toString() : '0'
          });
        }
      }

    } catch (error) {
      console.error('METARз‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪй–ҝж¬’оҮӨ:', error);
    }

    return parsed;
  }
}

// жӨӢеәЎеһҺй–Іеҝҡо…ёз» жҘҒж№ҮйҚ”?class WindComponentCalculator {
  // з’Ғпј„з•»з’әжҲҰдәҫжӨӢеәЎеһҺй–І?  static calculateWindComponents(windDirection: number, windSpeed: number, runwayHeading: number): { headwind: number; crosswind: number } {
    const angleDiff = Math.abs(windDirection - runwayHeading);
    const angleRad = (angleDiff * Math.PI) / 180;
    
    const headwind = Math.cos(angleRad) * windSpeed;
    const crosswind = Math.sin(angleRad) * windSpeed;
    
    return {
      headwind: Math.round(headwind * 10) / 10,
      crosswind: Math.round(Math.abs(crosswind) * 10) / 10
    };
  }
}

// жӨӢзӮ¶о”‘з‘ҷеӢ«еһҜйҚ’гӮ…з•„1Ө7
class FlightRulesCalculator {
  static getFlightRules(parsedMETAR: ParsedMETAR): string {
    const visibility = parseInt(parsedMETAR.visibility) || 9999;
    const clouds = parsedMETAR.clouds;
    
    let ceiling = 9999;
    for (const cloud of clouds) {
      if (cloud.type === 'BKN' || cloud.type === 'OVC') {
        const height = parseInt(cloud.height) || 9999;
        if (height < ceiling) {
          ceiling = height;
        }
      }
    }

    // VFRйҸүвўгІж¬ў
    if (visibility >= 5000 && ceiling >= 1000) {
      return 'VFR';
    }
    // MVFRйҸүвўгІж¬ў  
    else if (visibility >= 1500 && ceiling >= 500) {
      return 'MVFR';
    }
    // IFRйҸүвўгІж¬ў
    else if (visibility >= 800 && ceiling >= 200) {
      return 'IFR';
    }
    // LIFRйҸүвўгІж¬ў
    else {
      return 'LIFR';
    }
  }
}

// й‘ҫеі°еҪҮMETARйҸҒзүҲеөҒйҗЁеӢ«еҡұйҸҒжқҝз–„йҗң?- ж·ҮоҶҪж•јж¶“иҪ°зҙӯйҚҸе ңеЁҮйҗўг„ӨеҜҢйҸҒзүҲеөҒе©§?async function fetchMETARData(icao: string, config: Config): Promise<{ metar: string; taf: string }> {
  let metar = '';
  let taf = '';

  // жөјжЁәеҺӣжөЈи·Ёж•Өж¶“з»ҳжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°®
  const primarySource = API_SOURCES[config.primarySource];
  const otherSources = Object.values(API_SOURCES).filter(source => source.name !== config.primarySource);

  // жЈЈж §еҺӣзҒҸжҝҠзҳҜж¶“з»ҳжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°®
  if (primarySource) {
    try {
      if (config.consoleinfo) {
        console.log(`жөјжЁәеҺӣжө еәқеҜҢйҸҒзүҲеөҒе©§?${primarySource.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪ„1Ө7 ${icao} йҗЁеҮӘETARйҸҒзүҲеөҒ`);
      }

      const response = await axios.get(primarySource.metarUrl(icao), { timeout: 10000 });
      
      if (response.data) {
        const parsed = primarySource.parseMetar(response.data);
        if (parsed.metar) {
          metar = parsed.metar;
          taf = parsed.taf;
          
          // жҝЎеӮӣзҒүйҸҲеЎ—AFйҸҒзүҲеөҒй”ӣеұҪзҡҫз’ҮжӣЎе№ҸйҚҷж §з•¬йҸҒеҜёж®‘TAF
          if (!taf && primarySource.tafUrl) {
            try {
              const tafResponse = await axios.get(primarySource.tafUrl(icao), { timeout: 10000 });
              if (tafResponse.data && primarySource.parseTaf) {
                taf = primarySource.parseTaf(tafResponse.data);
              }
            } catch (tafError) {
              if (config.consoleinfo) {
                console.log(`жө еәқеҜҢйҸҒзүҲеөҒе©„1Ө7?${primarySource.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮTAFйҸҒзүҲеөҒжҫ¶иҫ«и§Ұ:`, tafError.message);
              }
            }
          }

          if (metar) {
            if (config.consoleinfo) {
              console.log(`йҺҙж„¬е§ӣжө еәқеҜҢйҸҒзүҲеөҒе©§?${primarySource.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮMETARйҸҒзүҲеө„1Ө7:`, metar);
            }
            return { metar, taf };
          }
        }
      }
    } catch (error) {
      if (config.consoleinfo) {
        console.log(`жө еәқеҜҢйҸҒзүҲеөҒе©„1Ө7?${primarySource.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮйҸҒзүҲеөҒжҫ¶иҫ«и§„1Ө7:`, error.message);
      }
    }
  }

  // ж¶“з»ҳжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°®жҫ¶иҫ«и§Ұй”ӣеұҪзҡҫз’ҮжӣһеҸҫжө ж ЁжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°„1Ө7
  for (const source of otherSources) {
    try {
      if (config.consoleinfo) {
        console.log(`зҒҸжҝҠзҳҜжө еәЎоҳ¬йҗўг„ҰжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°® ${source.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪ„1Ө7 ${icao} йҗЁеҮӘETARйҸҒзүҲеөҒ`);
      }

      const response = await axios.get(source.metarUrl(icao), { timeout: 10000 });
      
      if (response.data) {
        const parsed = source.parseMetar(response.data);
        if (parsed.metar) {
          metar = parsed.metar;
          taf = parsed.taf;
          
          // жҝЎеӮӣзҒүйҸҲеЎ—AFйҸҒзүҲеөҒй”ӣеұҪзҡҫз’ҮжӣЎе№ҸйҚҷж §з•¬йҸҒеҜёж®‘TAF
          if (!taf && source.tafUrl) {
            try {
              const tafResponse = await axios.get(source.tafUrl(icao), { timeout: 10000 });
              if (tafResponse.data && source.parseTaf) {
                taf = source.parseTaf(tafResponse.data);
              }
            } catch (tafError) {
              if (config.consoleinfo) {
                console.log(`жө еәЎоҳ¬йҗўг„ҰжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°„1Ө7 ${source.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮTAFйҸҒзүҲеөҒжҫ¶иҫ«и§Ұ:`, tafError.message);
              }
            }
          }

          if (metar) {
            if (config.consoleinfo) {
              console.log(`йҺҙж„¬е§ӣжө еәЎоҳ¬йҗўг„ҰжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°® ${source.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮMETARйҸҒзүҲеө„1Ө7:`, metar);
            }
            break;
          }
        }
      }
    } catch (error) {
      if (config.consoleinfo) {
        console.log(`жө еәЎоҳ¬йҗўг„ҰжҡҹйҺ№оҶҪз°„1Ө7 ${source.name} й‘ҫеі°еҪҮйҸҒзүҲеөҒжҫ¶иҫ«и§„1Ө7:`, error.message);
      }
      continue;
    }
  }

  return { metar, taf };
}

// йҸӮеӣЁж№°жқҲж’іеҡӯйҸҚз…ҺзҙЎйҚ–ж «ж®‘йҚ‘иҠҘжҡҹзўг№зӮөе№„1Ө7
function formatTextOutput(
  icao: string,
  metar: string,
  taf: string,
  parsedMETAR: ParsedMETAR,
  airportInfo: AirportInfo,
  flightRules: string,
  sunTimes: SunTimes,
  config: Config  // еЁЈиҜІе§һconfigйҚҷеӮӣжҡҹйҗўг„Өз°¬зјҲжҳҸзҳ„1Ө7
): string {
  const airportName = airportInfo ? `${airportInfo.cnName} (${airportInfo.enName})` : icao;
  const elevation = airportInfo ? `${airportInfo.elevationFt} ft` : 'йҸҲоҒҶз…„1Ө7';
  
  let output = `йҰғе°Ӣй”„1Ө7?йҸҲе“„жәўг ${icao} е§ҳж—Үи–„ж·Үв„ғдј…\n`;
  output += `йҰғжҗ· ${airportName}\n`;
  output += `йҰғжҗ№ еЁҙй”Ӣе«„1Ө7: ${elevation}\n\n`;
  
  output += `йҰғжҗі жӨӢзӮ¶о”‘з‘ҷеӢ«еһҜ: ${getFlightRulesEmoji(flightRules)} ${flightRules}\n`;
  output += `йҰғе°…й”„1Ө7?еЁ“в•Ғе®„1Ө7: ${parsedMETAR.temperature || 'N/A'}жҺіC\n`;
  output += `йҰғжҢ§ й—ҮиҢ¬еҒ„1Ө7: ${parsedMETAR.dewpoint || 'N/A'}жҺіC\n`;
  output += `йҰғжҗ№ й‘іеўгҹоқҶжҗ„1Ө7? ${parsedMETAR.visibility || 'N/A'} з»«з ӣn`;
  output += `йҰғжҢ© жӨӢеәЎжӮ„1Ө7: ${parsedMETAR.windDirection || 'N/A'}жҺ„1Ө7 жӨӢеәЁвӮ„1Ө7? ${parsedMETAR.windSpeed || '0'} ${parsedMETAR.windUnit || 'KT'}\n`;
  if (parsedMETAR.windGust) {
    output += `йҰғжҢ© й—ғз”ёо—„1Ө7: ${parsedMETAR.windGust} ${parsedMETAR.windUnit || 'KT'}\n`;
  }
  output += `йҰғжҗі е§ҳж–ҝеё„1Ө7: ${parsedMETAR.pressure || 'N/A'} ${ 'HPA'}\n\n`;
  
  // жөңжҲқзң°ж·Үв„ғдј… - жөЈи·Ёж•ӨйҸ„зҠІзҡ зҗӣг„§зӮ•з’Ү?  if (parsedMETAR.clouds.length > 0) {
    output += `йҲҪдҫҠз¬„1Ө7 жөңжҲқзң°ж·Үв„ғдј…:\n`;
    parsedMETAR.clouds.forEach(cloud => {
      const cloudDescription = config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === cloud.type)?.description || cloud.type;
      if (cloud.type === 'NSC' || cloud.type === 'SKC' || cloud.type === 'CLR') {
        output += `   - ${cloudDescription}\n`;
      } else {
        output += `   - ${cloudDescription} ${cloud.height} ft\n`;
      }
    });
  } else {
    output += `йҲҪвӮ¬й”„1Ө7?йҸғзҠіжЁүй’ҒжӨҫз°ҜзҒһдҝ“n`;
  }
  
  // жҫ¶в•ӮзҡөйҗңжӢҢи–„ - жөЈи·Ёж•ӨйҸ„зҠІзҡ зҗӣг„§зӮ•з’Ү?  if (parsedMETAR.weather.length > 0) {
    const weatherDescriptions = parsedMETAR.weather.map(code => {
      return config.weatherMap.find(item => item.code === code)?.description || code;
    });
    output += `йҰғе°Қй”„1Ө7?жҫ¶в•ӮзҡөйҗңжӢҢи–„: ${weatherDescriptions.join(', ')}\n`;
  }
  
  // йҸғгғҘеҡӯйҸғгғЁжғӨйҸғе •жЈ„1Ө7
  if (sunTimes) {
    output += `\nйҰғеҜҳ йҸғгғҘеҡ„1Ө7: ${sunTimes.sunrise} | йҰғеҜҡ йҸғгғЁжғ„1Ө7: ${sunTimes.sunset}\n`;
  }
  
  output += `\nйҰғж‘‘ METAR: ${metar}\n`;
  if (taf) {
    output += `йҰғж‘‘ TAF: ${taf}\n`;
  }
  
  return output;
}

// й‘ҫеі°еҪҮжӨӢзӮ¶о”‘з‘ҷеӢ«еһҜзўгөз‘°з°ІйҗЁеӢ®гўгғйҺҜе‘ҜоғҒйҚ„1Ө7?function getFlightRulesEmoji(flightRules: string): string {
  switch (flightRules) {
    case 'VFR': return 'йҰғз…қ';
    case 'MVFR': return 'йҰғж•ё';
    case 'IFR': return 'йҰғз…ӣ';
    case 'LIFR': return 'йҰғж•¶';
    default: return 'йҲ„1Ө7?;
  }
}

export function apply(ctx: Context, config: Config) {
  const command = ctx.command(`${config.commandname} <icao:string>`)
    .alias(config.commandalias)
    .action(async ({ session }, icao) => {
      if (!icao) {
        return 'з’Үз–Ҝз·ӯйҚҸгғҰжәҖйҚҰзҜ’CAOжө пҪҮзҲңй”ӣеұјз·ҘжҝЎеӮҰзҙ°metar ZBAA';
      }

      if (!/^[A-Z]{4}$/.test(icao.toUpperCase())) {
        return 'ICAOжө пҪҮзҲңйҸҚз…ҺзҙЎй–ҝж¬’оҮӨй”ӣеұҪз°Іж¶„1Ө7?ж¶“оҒ„гҒҮйҚҗж¬Ҹз“§е§Је¶Ҹзҙқжёҡе¬Әоӣ§й”ӣжӯ“BAA';
      }

      icao = icao.toUpperCase();

      try {
        // й‘ҫеі°еҪҮйҸҲе“„жәҖж·Үв„ғдј„1Ө7
        const airportInfo = await AirportService.getAirportInfo(icao);
        
        // йӘһжғ°о”‘й‘ҫеі°еҪҮйҚҸжңөзІ¬йҸҒзүҲеөҒ
        const [runways, metarData, sunTimes] = await Promise.all([
          AirportService.getRunways(icao),
          fetchMETARData(icao, config),
          airportInfo ? SunTimeService.getSunTimes(airportInfo.latitudeDeg, airportInfo.longitudeDeg, config) : Promise.resolve(null)
        ]);

        if (!metarData.metar) {
          return `йҸғзҠізЎ¶й‘ҫеі°еҪҮ ${icao} йҗЁеҮӘETARйҸҒзүҲеөҒ`;
        }

        // з‘ҷпҪҶзҖҪMETAR
        const parsedMETAR = METARParser.parse(metarData.metar);
        
        // з’Ғпј„з•»жӨӢеәЎеһҺй–Іеҝ“жӢ°жӨӢзӮ¶о”‘з‘ҷеӢ«еһ„1Ө7
        const windDirection = parseInt(parsedMETAR.windDirection) || 0;
        const windSpeed = parseInt(parsedMETAR.windSpeed) || 0;
        
        // з’Ғпј„з•»йҺөвӮ¬йҸҲеӨҺзӘҮй–¬ж’¶ж®‘жӨӢеәЎеһҺй–Іеҝ“иӢҹйҺёеӨҗвӮ¬е—ӣо—“йҚ’е—ӣеҷәйҺәжҺ‘з°ӯ
        let runwayWindComponents = runways.map(runway => {
          const heading = parseInt(runway.leHeadingDegt) || 0;
          return {
            runway,
            components: WindComponentCalculator.calculateWindComponents(windDirection, windSpeed, heading)
          };
        });

        // йҺёеӨҗвӮ¬е—ӣо—“йҚ’е—ӣеҷәжө еәЎгҒҮйҚ’жқҝзҡ¬йҺәжҺ‘з°ӯй”ӣе ҘвӮ¬е—ӣо—“жөјжЁәеҺӣй”ӣ?        runwayWindComponents.sort((a, b) => b.components.headwind - a.components.headwind);

        const flightRules = FlightRulesCalculator.getFlightRules(parsedMETAR);

        // ж·ҮоҶјоҳІй‘№еү§еЈ’йҗўг„Ұеҹӣй—ӮоҮўго•„1Ө7 - жөЈи·Ёж•Өе§қпҪҮвўгҳйҗЁеӢ¬зүёеҜ„1Ө7?        const userMention = session ? h('at', { id: session.userId }) : '';

        // йҸҚи§„еөҒжқҲж’іеҡӯеҰҜвўгізҙЎжқ©ж–ҝжҙ–зјҒж’ҙзҒү
        if (config.outputMode === 'text') {
          const textOutput = formatTextOutput(icao, metarData.metar, metarData.taf, parsedMETAR, airportInfo, flightRules, sunTimes, config);
          return userMention ? [userMention, textOutput] : textOutput;
        } else if (config.outputMode === 'image') {
          const imageOutput = await generateImageOutput(
            ctx, icao, metarData.metar, metarData.taf, parsedMETAR, 
            airportInfo, runways, runwayWindComponents, flightRules, config, sunTimes
          );
          // йҚҘеү§еў–еҰҜвҖізҙЎж¶“е¬©зҜғз‘•дҪҪеЈҳйҗ—еңӯж•ӨйҺҙ?          return userMention ? [userMention, imageOutput] : imageOutput;
        } else {
          const textOutput = formatTextOutput(icao, metarData.metar, metarData.taf, parsedMETAR, airportInfo, flightRules, sunTimes, config);
          const imageOutput = await generateImageOutput(
            ctx, icao, metarData.metar, metarData.taf, parsedMETAR,
            airportInfo, runways, runwayWindComponents, flightRules, config, sunTimes
          );
          // еЁЈеі°жӮҺеҰҜвҖізҙЎж¶“е¬©зҜғз‘•дҪҪеЈҳйҗ—еңӯж•ӨйҺҙ?          return userMention ? [userMention, textOutput, imageOutput] : [textOutput, imageOutput];
        }

      } catch (error) {
        if (config.consoleinfo) {
          console.error('е§ҳж—Үи–„йҸҢгғЁоҮ—й–ҝж¬’оҮ„1Ө7:', error);
        }
        return `йҸҢгғЁоҮ—е§ҳж—Үи–„йҸҒзүҲеөҒйҸғи·әеҡӯйҗңдјҙж•Ҡз’Ү? ${error.message}`;
      }
    });

  // йҚҘеү§еў–жқҲж’іеҡӯйҗўзҶёеһ„1Ө7
  async function generateImageOutput(
    ctx: Context, 
    icao: string, 
    metar: string, 
    taf: string, 
    parsedMETAR: ParsedMETAR,
    airportInfo: AirportInfo,
    runways: RunwayInfo[],
    runwayWindComponents: any[],
    flightRules: string,
    config: Config,
    sunTimes: SunTimes
  ) {
    // еҰ«вӮ¬йҸ„1Ө7?puppeteer йҸ„оҲҡжғҒйҚҷоҲңж•Ө
    if (!ctx.puppeteer) {
      const textOutput = formatTextOutput(icao, metar, taf, parsedMETAR, airportInfo, flightRules, sunTimes, config);
      return `йҚҘеү§еў–йҗўзҶёеһҡйҚ”зҶ»е…ҳй—ҮвӮ¬з‘•дҪёз•Ёз‘„1Ө7?puppeteer йҺ»жҺҚж¬ўй”ӣеұјдә’ж¶“е¬«ж§ёйҸӮеӣЁж№°йҸҚз…ҺзҙЎйҗЁеӢ¬зҡөз’һвўгІдҝҠйҺӯоҲӨзҙ°\n\n${textOutput}`;
    }

    try {
      const page = await ctx.puppeteer.page();
      
      // з’Ғеү§з–Ҷз‘ҷе——еҪӣжҫ¶Сғзҡ¬жө гғҰеҪҒжҘӮжЁ»з«»йҸ…жқҝе®„1Ө7
      if (config.imageMode === 'manual') {
        await page.setViewport({
          width: config.imageWidth,
          height: config.imageHeight,
          deviceScaleFactor: 2
        });
      } else {
        await page.setViewport({
          width: 1920,
          height: 1080,
          deviceScaleFactor: 2
        });
      }

      // йҚ’ж¶ҳзј“йҗңйўҒе”¬йҚ–ж «ж®‘HTMLйҚҗе‘ӯоҶ„1Ө7
      const htmlContent = createModernWeatherHTML(
        icao, metar, taf, parsedMETAR, airportInfo, 
        runways, runwayWindComponents, flightRules, config, sunTimes
      );

      // з’Ғеү§з–ҶжӨӨз”ёжҪ°йҚҗе‘ӯоҶ„1Ө7
      await page.setContent(htmlContent, { waitUntil: 'networkidle0' });

      // йҺҙоҒ„жөҳй–«еӨҗгўг„1Ө7
      const screenshotOptions: any = {
        type: 'jpeg',
        quality: config.screenshotquality,
        encoding: 'binary'
      };

      // з’Ғеү§з–ҶйҺҙоҒ„жөҳзҒҸе“„оҮ„1Ө7
      if (config.imageMode === 'manual') {
        screenshotOptions.clip = {
          x: 0,
          y: 0,
          width: config.imageWidth,
          height: config.imageHeight
        };
      } else {
        // й‘·оҒ„е§©еҰҜвҖізҙЎ - йҸҚи§„еөҒйҚҗе‘ӯоҶҗз’ӢеҶ©жҡЈжҫ¶Сғзҡ„1Ө7
        const element = await page.$('.weather-container');
        if (element) {
          const boundingBox = await element.boundingBox();
          if (boundingBox) {
            screenshotOptions.clip = {
              x: boundingBox.x,
              y: boundingBox.y,
              width: Math.ceil(boundingBox.width),
              height: Math.ceil(boundingBox.height)
            };
          }
        }
      }

      // йҺҙоҒ„жө„1Ө7
      const screenshot = await page.screenshot(screenshotOptions) as unknown as Buffer;

      // йҚҸжҠҪжЈҙжӨӨз”ёжҪ°й”ӣе қоӣ§йҸӢж»ғжғҺйҗўг„ЁеҡңйҚ”г„ҘеҸ§й—Ӯо…Ёзҙ„1Ө7
      if (config.pageautoclose) {
        await page.close();
      }

      return h.image(screenshot, 'image/jpeg');

    } catch (error) {
      if (config.consoleinfo) {
        console.error('йҚҘеү§еў–йҗўзҶёеһҡй–ҝж¬’оҮ„1Ө7:', error);
      }
      // йҚҘеү§еў–йҗўзҶёеһҡжҫ¶иҫ«и§ҰйҸғи·әжҙ–й–«вӮ¬йҚ’зүҲжһғйҸҲо„ғз·ӯйҚ„1Ө7?      const textOutput = formatTextOutput(icao, metar, taf, parsedMETAR, airportInfo, flightRules, sunTimes, config);
      return `йҗўзҶёеһҡйҚҘеү§еў–йҸғи·әеҡӯйҗңдјҙж•Ҡз’ҮоҲӨзҙқжө гғӨз¬…йҸ„оҲӣжһғйҸҲо„ҒзүёеҜ®еҝ•ж®‘е§ҳж—Үи–„ж·Үв„ғдј…й”ӣжӯ•n\n${textOutput}`;
    }
  }

  let cachedWindSvgDataUri: string | null | undefined;
  function getWindSvgDataUri(): string | null {
    if (cachedWindSvgDataUri !== undefined) return cachedWindSvgDataUri;

    const candidates = [
      path.join(__dirname, 'wind.svg'),
      path.join(__dirname, '../src/wind.svg'),
      path.join(__dirname, '../dist/wind.svg'),
    ];

    for (const filePath of candidates) {
      try {
        if (!fs.existsSync(filePath)) continue;
        const svg = fs.readFileSync(filePath);
        cachedWindSvgDataUri = `data:image/svg+xml;base64,${svg.toString('base64')}`;
        return cachedWindSvgDataUri;
      } catch {
        // ignore and try next candidate
      }
    }

    cachedWindSvgDataUri = null;
    return cachedWindSvgDataUri;
  }

