  // й‘ҫеі°еҪҮжөңжҲқзң°йҗҳиҲөвӮ¬дҪ№ејҝжқ©?- жөЈи·Ёж•ӨйҸ„зҠІзҡ зҗӣг„§зӮ•з’Ү?  function getCloudCondition(clouds: any[], config: Config): string {
    if (clouds.length === 0) {
      return config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === 'NSC')?.description || "йҸғзҠіжЁүй’ҒжӨҫз°ҜзҒ„1Ө7?;
    }
    
    const hasOvercast = clouds.some(c => c.type === 'OVC');
    const hasBroken = clouds.some(c => c.type === 'BKN');
    const hasScattered = clouds.some(c => c.type === 'SCT');
    const hasFew = clouds.some(c => c.type === 'FEW');
    
    if (hasOvercast) return config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === 'OVC')?.description || "е©ҠвўгігҒүжө„1Ө7?;
    if (hasBroken) return config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === 'BKN')?.description || "жҫ¶ж°«з°„1Ө7";
    if (hasScattered) return config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === 'SCT')?.description || "йҗӨеҝҺз°„1Ө7";
    if (hasFew) return config.cloudCoverageMap.find(item => item.code === 'FEW')?.description || "зҒҸжҲңз°„1Ө7";
    
    return "йҸҲеӨүз°„1Ө7";
  }

  // йҗңйўҒе”¬йҚ–ж «ж®‘жҫ¶в•ӮзҡөйҚҘзӮ¬зҲЈй‘ҫеі°еҪ„1Ө7 - жөЈи·Ёж•ӨйҸ„зҠІзҡ зҗӣг„§зӮ•з’Ү?  function getModernWeatherIcon(weather: string[], clouds: any[], config: Config): string {
    // жЈЈж §еҺӣеҰ«вӮ¬йҸҢгғҰж§ёйҚҡпёҪж№Ғйҗ—и§„з•©жҫ¶в•ӮзҡөйҗңжӢҢи–„
    if (weather.some(w => config.weatherMap.find(item => item.code === w)?.description.includes('й—Ҷй”ӢжҜ„1Ө7'))) {
      return 'йүўге ¬з¬Қ';
    } else if (weather.some(w => config.weatherMap.find(item => item.code === w)?.description.includes('й—„1Ө7?))) {
      return 'йҰғе°Һй”„1Ө7?;
    } else if (weather.some(w => config.weatherMap.find(item => item.code === w)?.description.includes('й—„1Ө7?))) {
      return 'йүӮеӢ¶з¬„1Ө7';
    } else if (weather.some(w => config.weatherMap.find(item => item.code === w)?.description.includes('й—„1Ө7?))) {
      return 'йҰғе°—й”„1Ө7?;
    }
    
    // йҗ’и·әжӮ—йҸҚи§„еөҒжөңжҲҰеҷәйҚҗеҶІз•ҫ
    if (clouds.some(c => c.type === 'OVC')) {
      return 'йҲҪдҫҠз¬„1Ө7';
    } else if (clouds.some(c => c.type === 'BKN')) {
      return 'йҰғе°Ӣй”„1Ө7?;
    } else if (clouds.some(c => c.type === 'SCT') || clouds.some(c => c.type === 'FEW')) {
      return 'йүўг?;
    } else {
      return 'йҲҪвӮ¬й”„1Ө7?;
    }
  }

  // йҗңйўҒе”¬йҚ–ж «ж®‘з‘ҷеӮӣзҘҙйҸӮеӣЁж№°йҗўзҶёеһ„1Ө7 - жөЈи·Ёж•ӨйҸ„зҠІзҡ зҗӣг„§зӮ•з’Ү?  function generateModernObservationText(parsedMETAR: ParsedMETAR, humidity: string, config: Config): string {
    const windText = parsedMETAR.windDirection === 'VRB' ? 
      `жӨӢеәЎжӮңжҫ¶ж°¬еҪүй”ӣеІ„о—“й–«?${parsedMETAR.windSpeed} ${parsedMETAR.windUnit}` :
